    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "`expectRevert` with no parameters expects a `revert()` (i.e. a revert with no message). You should expect the `AccessControlViolation` error.\r\n\r\nSee the [book](https://book.getfoundry.sh/cheatcodes/expect-revert.html) for examples and docs, more specifically, you probably want something like the example in the book:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\ncheats.expectRevert(\r\n    abi.encodeWithSelector(MyContract.CustomError.selector, 1, 2)\r\n);\r\n```",
